{"tid":1561974,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"「願榮光歸香港」係香港國歌！\"Glory to Hong Kong\" is our national anthem!","createTime":"2019-09-11T23:17:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T01:29:13.000Z","uid":116526,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"57e7eb28bf1269af5b36db3a6af49e4d73042bd0","tid":1561974,"uid":116526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T23:17:01.000Z","msg":"我話你聽依首歌就係<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港國歌！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">&quot;Glory to Hong Kong&quot; is Hong Kong's national anthem!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n試問香港有邊首歌會聽到大家感動眼濕濕<br />\n自問咁大個人終於感受到人地國家聽到國歌會感動既感覺<br />\n連續幾晚各區商場都咁集到多人唱 係香港都係史無前例<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n啲大中華左膠 話乜鳩驚港獨既唔該一齊屌撚死班仆街<br />\n反正係咪都比人話港獨嫁啦！驚鳩咩？港共中共又可以做得啲乜？ 係咪都打壓緊嫁啦！ 驚就唔叫？叫國歌兩隻都驚 咁過去依3個月都唔洗出黎抗爭啦！<br />\n<br />\n抗共係唯一出路！香港做左幾代順民 港豬係時候要變！有首國歌已經係溫和曲線暗示宣傳 慢慢散播種子又易入口。反正都咁多人入左腦入左屋，緊係食住上！<br />\n<br />\n連外媒都幫我地宣傳首歌係香港國歌，點解仲有啲左膠咁撚on9 矮化自己？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後：<br />\n<br />\n黎明來到　要光復　這香港<br />\n同行兒女　為正義　時代革命<br />\n祈求　民主與自由　萬世都不朽<br />\n我願榮光歸香港<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n五大訴求<br />\n缺一不可</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"4e7283e0a22dfbfab5e3c77748d21d69a749d3e0","tid":1561974,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T23:17:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"de695184feda4baa10b47182d26fdf93d2ea5a2c","tid":1561974,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T23:17:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"ce105234ab4041abde4d3a02ac6cce7970cd700d","tid":1561974,"uid":116526,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T23:17:25.000Z","msg":"大中華左膠收皮！"},{"pid":"434f58149572840c659715cd55ea1596afd6fbff","tid":1561974,"uid":116526,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T23:28:20.000Z","msg":"唔好再比左膠矮化！"},{"pid":"ffbd719d6225bfecbb147cb77da0a2f9a400d047","tid":1561974,"uid":116526,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T00:03:44.000Z","msg":"拒絕左膠"},{"pid":"13b52e5cab542a1fa76c35a507a11a675aa03899","tid":1561974,"uid":116526,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T00:35:21.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"55f181acf9b6448491270bba603fe67b748675c4","tid":1561974,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T00:35:29.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">對準政權 遍地開花</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b2D3bRU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb2D3bRU.jpg&h=49b546b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dXuufm1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdXuufm1.jpg&h=98681984&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yM2WNBw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyM2WNBw.jpg&h=9433ed2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zasf29R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A